  "body_excerpt": "<div>A security vulnerability has been identified in the AsusPTPFilter driver that could potentially affect touchpad functionality.<br />To address this issue, ASUS has released an important security update. Users are recommended to update the AsusPTPFilter driver to version 16.0.0.46 (or later), which will be automatically delivered through Windows Update.</div>\n<p style=\"background: white;\"><a href=\"https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2026-6737\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CVE-2026-6737</a><br />CVSS 4.0 Score： 2.0/Low<br />AV:L/AC:H/AT:P/PR:L/UI:N/VC:L/VI:N/VA:L/SC:N/SI:N/SA:N</p>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>",
